<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPORTS-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
 ATTN Sports Editors:  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for SUNDAY,
July 16.
</P>
<P>
   BOYS-LIPSYTE-COLUMN (Undated) _ Robert Lipsyte on the incident
in Massachusetts in which one father killed another in a dispute
