<P>
   ARIZONA CARDINALS
</P>
<P>
   PLAYERS REPORT: Friday, Northern Arizona University, Flagstaff,
Ariz.
</P>
<P>
   1999: 6-10, 4th in NFC East
</P>
<P>
   KEY ADDITIONS: PK Cary Blanchard, DT Tony McCoy, TE Chris Gedney
</P>
<P>
   KEY LOSSES: DE Eric Swann, RB Adrian Murrell
</P>
<P>
   THINGS TO DO: Get DE Simeon Rice to stop sulking; decide if
first-round draft pick Thomas Jones or third-year incumbent Michael
Pittman is team's top RB; get Jake Plummer back to 1998 form.
</P>
<P>
   PRESEASON SCHEDULE Aug. 5 Denver 9 p.m. Aug. 12 Seattle 9 p.m.
Aug. 18 at Minnesota 7:20 p.m. Aug. 25 at San Diego 9 p.m.
ATLANTA FALCONS
</P>
