Claridge (rookie), WR Shawn Jefferson
</P>
<P>
   KEY LOSSES: DE Lester Archambeau, WR Chris Calloway, DE Chuck
Smith, C/G Robbie Tobeck
</P>
<P>
   THINGS TO DO: Make sure Jamal Anderson is healthy after knee
injury. Establish cohesiveness on revamped offensive line.
Compensate for loss of Chuck Smith and Lester Archambeau, longtime
starters at defensive end.
</P>
<P>
   PRESEASON SCHEDULE July 29 at Indianapolis 7 p.m. Aug. 5 vs.
Dallas 9 p.m. Aug. 11 Cincinnati 6:30 p.m. Aug. 18 San Diego 6:30
p.m. Aug. 24 at Jacksonville 6:30 p.m. _at Tokyo
