<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-15 23:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3457 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BBO-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     07-15 0679
